snippet.title: Geometry - Triangle Congruence (ASA, AAS)
snippet.description:
When mathematicians have a sway in their step, they are called mathemaLIMPINz. Join the mathemaLIMPIN as we explore two rules that make triangles congruent: ASA and AAS. Good vibes in the class on this one, YAY MATH!

Learning should always be fun and connective. Please visit http://www.yaymath.org for:
• all videos
• free quizzes
• free worksheets
• debut book on how to connect with and inspire students
• all-in-one math courses that teachers and parents can use, backed by Yay Math energy
